<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>the following code generate an invalid select column</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
// ...
$dbSelect-&gt;joinInner(
    array($tableAs =&gt; $table),
    $where,
    null
);
// -&gt; SELECT [.....]  `myTableAs`.``, .[....]  FROM [.....]
//      `myTableAs`.``  is wrong
</code></pre>

<p>but the following success</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
// ...
$dbSelect-&gt;joinInner(
    array($tableAs =&gt; $table),
    $where,
    array()
);
</code></pre>

